{
  "stem": "1684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My role was, first of all, I played handball.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to other cities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We played against others like here, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We played against other cities and against other sport clubs, against [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], And we were from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we played against each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were-- every Sunday we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was like, in [NON-ENGLISH], there was a sport-- a very big sport park.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we came there every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the week, we were busy with, you know, with working and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was-- was nice until 1937, 1938, it was already a little bit different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in 1938, I don't know whether you heard about the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you, with my brothers and sisters, we had a very good relationship, because my brothers were older than me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only problem I had with them is when we went out and somebody wanted to make a date with me, they had a very hard time to-- to accepting that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They investigated, and always they said to me, don't go out with this guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I heard them talk about girls, so I always felt that if I get into some situation, [INAUDIBLE] about it would be terrible.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I always was careful with whom I dated too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and I had a lot of-- I mean, I had a lot of asking to be dated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a hard time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 16 and 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, when I was 16 years old, the [NON-ENGLISH], the leader of one of the group from [INAUDIBLE] who came to play against us in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was from Dresden.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
